You figure out how the user navigates our web and app applications, find the pain points and help wrinkle them out. Google Analytics and A/B testing tools like Optimizely are some of the toolings you are using to get the data. You know that data does not just fall from the sky (or from a tracking script) so you are tech savvy enough to identify, track, and use the data you need to optimize the user experience.
